title: HS Hoops Star Hansel Enmanuel Joins the Show
description:
Jalen & Jacoby discuss what makes the Mavs dangerous. Jacoby is adamant that LeBron’s dunk on Kevin Love was NOT a poster. Did they Falcons make a mistake trade Matt Ryan to the Colts? AND we celebrate the beauty of Pusha-T’s Arby’s diss track. THEN high school phenom Hansel Enmanuel joins the show to talk about his basketball future, and who he models his game after.
